method.name: getName

method.description: Returns the transitive ResolvedDependency instances of this resolved dependency. Returns never null.

method.name: getAllModuleArtifacts
method.description:
Returns the module artifacts belonging to this ResolvedDependency and recursively to its children. Returns never null.
@see #getModuleArtifacts()

method.name: getModuleVersion
method.description: Returns the module version of the resolved dependency.

method.description:
Returns the module which this resolved dependency belongs to.

returns:The module.
